data.event: Anda comprises 16 barangays: The municipality of Anda was formerly known as Quinale and was a barrio of the municipality of Guindulman from the early part of its civilization up to the later decades of the 19th century.

event.title: years the population of Quinale grew

data.event: Through the years the population of Quinale grew and the people sought independence from Guindulman.
On July 8, 1856 they petitioned for independence and the petition was endorsed by the Assessor General of the Government to the Governor General of the Philippines on September 3, 1856.
